org.jwave.model.playlist

Interface PlaylistManager

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    PlaylistManagerImpl

    public interface PlaylistManager
    Interface that models the concept of playlist manager. A playlist manager manages playlists and contains the strategy for navigating them.
